net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data

Class SimpleListModel<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data.AbstractListModel
      • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data.SimpleListModel<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the list element type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.util.List<E>, ListModel
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DragAndDropListModelImpl

    public class SimpleListModel<E>
extends AbstractListModel
implements java.util.List<E>
    List model that uses a List object. This class implements List, therefore the preferred method of updating the underlying list is using the List interface on the model. If the underlying List is changed otherwise, the developer is responsible for calling the correct event firing methods in the superclass! ( AbstractListModel.fireContentsChanged(), etc. )
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
